---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - Mobile Veterinary Services Bundaberg"
  description="Learn about Dr Heidi's Mobile Veterinary Services in Bundaberg. Our dedicated team provides professional, affordable pet care with a caring approach. We've been serving the Bundaberg community for years."
  keywords="about Dr Heidi's mobile vet, veterinary team Bundaberg, pet care Bundaberg, local vet Bundaberg, community vet services"
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-secondary-50 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          About Dr Heidi's Mobile Veterinary Services
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We care for them because they love you
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main About Section -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6234612/pexels-photo-6234612.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=600"
            alt="Veterinary team with animals in Bundaberg clinic"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Our Dedicated Team is Always Here for Your Pets
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our Veterinary Hospital provides modern, professional and affordable health care for your pets. We aim to make your pet feel at ease in our clinic with a caring and gentle approach to treatment and consultations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our dedicated staff and leading veterinarians are all passionate about pets and avid animal lovers. We understand the special bond between you and your companion, and we're committed to providing the highest standard of care.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sound Advice Section -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                Sound Advice First and Foremost
              </h2>
              <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                At our Veterinary Hospital in Bundaberg, you'll be fully supported with sound advice first and foremost. We know that helping our clients starts with providing a good understanding of health care issues and treatment options.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                With good advice and professional recommendations, you'll be well equipped to make the best ongoing health care decisions for your pet. We believe in empowering pet owners with knowledge and understanding.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Facilities Section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Fully Equipped for Your Pet's Needs
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            With fully equipped examination rooms, diagnostic machines and pharmaceutical stores we provide on-the-spot assistance for nearly all pet health and medical needs across Bundaberg and surrounding areas.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Take a moment to meet our team and our own pets. We look forward to seeing you and your pet again at the next scheduled visit in Bundaberg.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Modern Equipment</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">State-of-the-art diagnostic tools</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Examination Rooms</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Comfortable and clean spaces</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pharmaceutical Store</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">On-site medications available</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Mobile Services</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">We come to you in Bundaberg</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-first lg:order-last">
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6235120/pexels-photo-6235120.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=600"
            alt="Veterinary clinic examination room in Bundaberg"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Integration Section -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-50 to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            A Big Part of Our Local Community
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our Veterinary Hospital has been an integral part of our local community in Bundaberg for years. In that time, we've helped thousands of our clients' cats & dogs, rabbits & guinea pigs, birds, horses and even a few snakes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Being so strongly integrated with our local community in Bundaberg is important to us and our clients. Our customers know by experience that they can rely on us for sound advice and treatment options and that their pet is in the very best hands with our team.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1000+</div>
              <div class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Happy Clients</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">8+</div>
              <div class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Pet Species</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">24/7</div>
              <div class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Emergency Care</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">100%</div>
              <div class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Dedicated Care</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-600">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6">
        Experience the Difference
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-primary-50 mb-6 sm:mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join thousands of satisfied pet owners in Bundaberg who trust us with their pets' health
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-primary font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all"
        >
          Contact Us Today
        </a>
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 bg-secondary hover:bg-secondary-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all"
        >
          View Our Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
